trans-unit.source: The StripLinesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects, and is implemented as the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> class.
trans-unit.target: StripLinesCollection 類別表示的<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>物件，並實作為<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>類別</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>的屬性</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>集合

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects can be appended, inserted or removed from the collection at both design time and run time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>物件可以附加、 插入或移除在設計階段和執行的階段集合中。</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>

trans-unit.source: **Note** Strip lines can be displayed once or repeatedly for a set interval.
trans-unit.target: **請注意**帶狀線可能會顯示一次或重複在設定的間隔。
